      <p class="longform-body">You're watching a show in your target language. Someone says a word you don't know. By the time you open a flashcard app, find the right deck, create a card, write the definition... the moment is gone. And so is the word.</p>
      <p class="longform-body">LanguageDen's Quick Notes let you type or record audio in seconds. Just capture the word and move on. Later, process your notes into full flashcards with a tap.</p>
      <p class="longform-body">Nothing gets lost. Every word you encounter becomes a word you can learn.</p>
    </div>
