      <p class="longform-body">Research consistently shows that pairing words with images dramatically improves recall. It's called the "picture superiority effect." Your brain remembers images far better than text alone.</p>
      <p class="longform-body">LanguageDen has built-in Unsplash image search. Find a relevant photo and attach it to any card. When you review, that visual anchor helps the word stick in ways that pure text never will.</p>
