          <h3>Is it really free?</h3>
          <p>Yes. LanguageDen is free to download and free to use. No subscription, no paywall, no "premium" features locked behind a monthly fee. The free version will always be free.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What is FSRS?</h3>
          <p>FSRS (Free Spaced Repetition Scheduler) is a modern, open-source algorithm for scheduling flashcard reviews. It's more accurate than the SM-2 algorithm that Anki has used for decades. It adapts to your memory patterns and shows you cards right before you'd forget them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Does it have AI features?</h3>
          <p>Yes, as an optional extra. You can connect an OpenRouter API key to auto-generate flashcard content like definitions, example sentences, and conjugations. But the app is fully functional without it. AI is a convenience, not a requirement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What languages are supported?</h3>
          <p>All of them. If you can type it, LanguageDen supports it. There's no fixed language list. The app works with any writing system and any language.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I import my Anki decks?</h3>
